*Požurite* da završite posao (Hurry up to finish the job).
*Pogurajte* malo brže (Push a bit faster).
*Požurite* da stignete na vreme (Hurry up to arrive on time).
*Požuri* da sve bude spremno (Hurry up to have everything ready).
*Požurila* je da se što pre vrati kući (She hurried up to get home as soon as possible).